un &lt;dan keyn shterers&gt; s'iz nit geven, flegn mir hern fray zayne redes.

00:10:08.568 --> 00:10:09.605
zayne un Gebels',

00:10:09.605 --> 00:10:11.748
hot &lt;dan gemoldn&gt; zeyer &lt;breytlekh oysgehern&gt; zikh.

00:10:11.748 --> 00:10:13.570
un tsu tsvey sho flegt men

00:10:13.570 --> 00:10:16.074
di radyo ibergebn nor zayne redes.

00:10:17.345 --> 00:10:20.321
in zeks un draysikstn yor iz geven in Shavl,

00:10:20.321 --> 00:10:21.170
in Lite,

00:10:21.716 --> 00:10:22.880
a bafelkerung

00:10:22.880 --> 00:10:25.001
iber- b- ibergeshribn di bafelkerung.

00:10:25.310 --> 00:10:26.919
iz dan in Shavl geven

00:10:26.930 --> 00:10:29.827
tsvelf, tsvelf a halb toyznt yidn hobn gelebt in Shavl.

00:10:30.035 --> 00:10:33.742
&lt;tsvishn&gt; dray un draysik toyznt mentshn in gantsn hobn gelebt tsvelf, tsvelf a halb toyznt yidn.

00:10:34.625 --> 00:10:36.411
aza tsore iz geven aza protsent yidn

00:10:36.411 --> 00:10:37.371
in Shavl.

00:10:38.912 --> 00:10:44.115
in zeks un draysikstn yor, nokhn &lt;ibershraybn&gt; di ge- bafelkerung iz gekumen Sha- Shabotinski.

00:10:44.115 --> 00:10:46.263
rikhtik, iz Zhabotinski, nit Shabotinski.

00:10:46.320 --> 00:10:48.536
iz er gekumen in Shavl

00:10:48.547 --> 00:10:49.270
un er hot f-

00:10:49.270 --> 00:10:50.206
gelozn durkh v-

00:10:50.206 --> 00:10:52.771
durkhn rov meldn az ir zolt, vifl me ken zol kumen

00:10:52.771 --> 00:10:56.472
in groyse khor-shul, iz gekumen zeyer a sakh mentshn oyfn geheft, vayl s'iz geven zumer.

00:10:56.883 --> 00:10:57.935
azoy gedenk ikh.

00:10:57.935 --> 00:11:00.809
&lt;kolosale&gt; sakh mentshn, &lt;kh'gleyb,&gt; un m'hot gezogt "raboysay,

00:11:01.187 --> 00:11:04.134
es tsit zikh oyf undz a shvartser volkn.

00:11:05.169 --> 00:11:07.863
loyft fun danet ver hot di meglekhkeyt.

00:11:09.405 --> 00:11:10.918
vayle der soyne iz noent

00:11:11.801 --> 00:11:12.993
un der soyne iz

00:11:13.050 --> 00:11:14.479
zeyer a shreklekher."

00:11:16.239 --> 00:11:17.490
iz vi loyfn?

00:11:17.490 --> 00:11:19.257
di raykhe mentshn hobn gekent loyfn,

00:11:19.257 --> 00:11:20.877
hobn zey gekent iberlozn zeyer

00:11:20.877 --> 00:11:21.729
raykhkeyt.

00:11:21.740 --> 00:11:25.492
di oreme, ot azoy vi mir un nokh azelkhe, di merste iz geven oreme, di merste,

00:11:25.492 --> 00:11:27.354
hobn mir nit gehat vos aroystsuforn.

00:11:28.136 --> 00:11:30.645
hot zikh ongefangen in Shavl organizirn kholutsim.

00:11:32.051 --> 00:11:34.411
kholutsim, mistame &lt;veysn&gt; ver dos iz geven.

00:11:34.411 --> 00:11:35.810
ir veyst nit ver iz geven kholutsim?

00:11:35.055 --> 00:11:37.024
nu, nu, zogt a bisele.

00:11:36.506 --> 00:11:39.440
dos iz geven yunge yinglekh mit meydlekh, oreme kinder,

00:11:39.440 --> 00:11:41.591
hobn zikh ongefangen lernen landvirt-arbet.

00:11:41.591 --> 00:11:43.127
landvirtshaftlekhe arbet.

00:11:43.172 --> 00:11:45.498
flegt men geyn un forn oyf, dort bay di landvirtn

00:11:45.498 --> 00:11:49.118
arbetn un glaykhtsaytik iz zikh kenen oyslernen vi baarbetn di erd.

00:11:49.118 --> 00:11:51.098
iz kedey me zol kumendik in Palestine,

00:11:51.680 --> 00:11:53.125
dan iz geven eyn lozung zayner,

00:11:53.125 --> 00:11:55.602
nor in Palestine, dos hayntike Erets-Yisroel

00:11:55.980 --> 00:12:00.483
kumen, me zol shoyn hobn m- mer oder veyniker a farshtand vos heyst an aker-ayzn,

00:12:00.483 --> 00:12:02.010
un vos heyst a kose,

00:12:02.010 --> 00:12:02.938
un andere,

00:12:02.938 --> 00:12:06.285
andere getsayg vos me darf bayn arbetn di ar- di lan- di erd.

00:12:06.965 --> 00:12:09.491
vayl &lt;dos UNK iz dos yunge&gt; hot nit gevust di zakhn.

00:12:09.598 --> 00:12:11.274
hot zikh &lt;ongefangen&gt; umruikn.

00:12:11.274 --> 00:12:15.147
a sakh litvishe yunge mentshn flegn blaybn on arbet; di flegn forn

00:12:15.147 --> 00:12:17.079
arbetn nor kedey zikh oystsulernen

00:12:17.079 --> 00:12:20.390
arbet, land-arbet, flegn zey nit fodern keyn groyse batsolungen.

00:12:20.853 --> 00:12:23.424
UNK s'iz zeyer bilik in getsolt, me flegt tsoln in gantsn

00:12:23.452 --> 00:12:24.881
dray fir lit a tog

00:12:24.954 --> 00:12:27.027
farn arbet, nor dos zey &lt;hobn&gt; gefodert kedey

00:12:27.027 --> 00:12:29.893
umgefer &lt;oyf&gt; fardinen etlekhe lit i- oyf di veg hobn.

00:12:29.983 --> 00:12:33.487
s'hot gefodert umgefer bay tsvey hundert lit me zol kenen aroysforn in oysland.

00:12:33.932 --> 00:12:34.942
me zol UNK,

00:12:34.942 --> 00:12:37.234
nor leyder un der, di merste hot dos oykh nit gehat.

00:12:38.741 --> 00:12:40.282
azoy hot zikh getsoygn epes

00:12:40.327 --> 00:12:41.756
a tsvey yor tsayt.

00:12:42.926 --> 00:12:45.857
nokh UNK vos di kholutsim, iz gevorn shtil mit di kholutsim.

00:12:46.031 --> 00:12:49.260
tsu, &lt;m'iz nit arayngeloz-&gt; dan der der mandat, der, Erets-Yisroel hot gehat di englander,

00:12:49.260 --> 00:12:51.099
di englen- England hobn gehat dem mandat

00:12:51.127 --> 00:12:53.290
un zey hobn nit arayngelozn in k-

00:12:53.630 --> 00:12:56.117
shv-, geven groyse shverikeytn araynforn in Erets-Yisroel.

00:12:56.612 --> 00:12:58.979
azoy iz durkhgelofn di kurtse tsayt,

00:12:58.979 --> 00:13:00.971
un dos, Hitler unterdesn hot farnumen glaykh

00:13:00.971 --> 00:13:04.233
Estraykh. nakher nokh Estraykh iz gefaln a korbn Tshekhoslovakay,

00:13:04.307 --> 00:13:07.440
un iz durkhgegangen biz nayn un draysikstn yor di blutike krig in Poyln.

00:13:07.614 --> 00:13:09.026
biz farnemen Poyln

00:13:09.183 --> 00:13:13.329
hot zikh nit gelozt hern az me zol hargenen yidn, nor vi er hot farnumen Poyln hot zikh shoyn ongefangen glay-, lang...

00:13:14.921 --> 00:13:17.919
ikh vil aykh fregn, efsher gegangen in kloyz?

00:13:19.106 --> 00:13:21.092
ir gegangen in kloyz far...

00:13:20.420 --> 00:13:22.712
shabes fleg ikh geyn in kloyz, ye. nor shabes.

00:13:22.903 --> 00:13:24.580
shabes, flegn mir &lt;avek&gt;, ye.

00:13:23.898 --> 00:13:27.858
 vu ir gelebt? in eygene dire, in shtub, vos heyst...

00:13:27.020 --> 00:13:29.228
mir hobn gehat a shtibl, an eygene shtibl.

00:13:29.228 --> 00:13:31.368
Shavl, Riger gas akhtsn.

00:13:32.302 --> 00:13:35.924
ir gelebt ale tsuzamen mit bruder mit shvester in...

00:13:33.866 --> 00:13:35.006
ale tsuzamen.

00:13:35.370 --> 00:13:36.296
di mame,

00:13:36.352 --> 00:13:40.440
der bruder un zayn froy, zayne dray kinderlekh, hobn mir ale tsuzamengelebt, ye.

00:13:40.689 --> 00:13:43.383
vos ir gemakht in, in a fraye tsayt?

00:13:43.710 --> 00:13:48.446
vos ir gehat holt, holt tsu makhn in fraye tsayt, vos ir gemakht?

00:13:48.249 --> 00:13:50.994
di fraye tsayt hobn mir gehat a shtikl erd lebn shtub.

00:13:51.894 --> 00:13:52.667
fleg ikh

00:13:52.670 --> 00:13:53.672
in gortn,

00:13:53.717 --> 00:13:54.926
in gortn flegn mir

00:13:55.218 --> 00:13:58.253
farzeyen un nakher poleven, opreynikn dem gortn.

00:13:58.256 --> 00:14:00.490
ot dos &lt;vayzt oys&gt;, zol zayn &lt;vi es heyst,&gt;

00:14:00.490 --> 00:14:03.797
a bisl b- laykhter der durkhtsulebn. flegn mir zikh oyfhodeven eyde-

00:14:03.797 --> 00:14:06.452
eygene grinsn oyfhodeven.

00:14:11.250 --> 00:14:15.666
UND, UND azoy gekumen di ershte tog fun milkhome bay aykh.

00:14:15.333 --> 00:14:15.985
ye.

00:14:16.295 --> 00:14:17.150
dos iz

00:14:19.046 --> 00:14:21.470
azoy bi- vi ikh itster hob aykh dertseylt,

00:14:21.678 --> 00:14:26.178
nakher bizn fertsikstn yor hob ikh, vi ikh hob aykh, ikh vel a tsveytn mol dermonen, hob ikh gearbet baym balebos.

00:14:23.670 --> 00:14:25.031
.

00:14:27.855 --> 00:14:29.199
fertsikstn yor, s'iz arayn

00:14:29.272 --> 00:14:30.957
di, di royte armey,

00:14:30.960 --> 00:14:34.425
hot men alts anulirt, bin ikh ariber arbetn in fabrik. hob ikh dortn gearbet umgefer

00:14:34.425 --> 00:14:36.360
akht nayn monat in gantsn, vayle glaykh iz g-,

00:14:36.360 --> 00:14:37.530
der eyn un fertsikstn yor

00:14:37.530 --> 00:14:40.151
dem tsvey un tsvantsikstn yuni iz shoyn oysgebrokhn di krig.

00:14:40.865 --> 00:14:42.845
di ershte blut vos mir &lt;hobn&gt; derzen,

00:14:42.845 --> 00:14:43.813
zuntik,

00:14:44.713 --> 00:14:47.812
undzer a shokhn Simkhele Lurye hot gefirt a ku in feld.

00:14:47.970 --> 00:14:50.040
dos, &lt;mit dos hot er farlebt&gt;, fun di ku.

00:14:50.349 --> 00:14:53.704
ongeforn a soldatske mashin mit farvundete gefirt fun front,

00:14:53.724 --> 00:14:55.628
fun Tavriger zayt iz ongeforn shoyn

00:14:55.628 --> 00:14:57.128
mashines mit farvundete.

00:14:57.453 --> 00:14:59.793
un der soldat hot gefregt di veg oyf Rige.

00:15:00.103 --> 00:15:01.802
nu, geveyntlekh hot er gevizn.

00:15:02.111 --> 00:15:03.627
vi di mashin iz avekgeforn

00:15:03.627 --> 00:15:07.049
hot zayner a shokhn im derharget mitn ayzn vos me bindt tsu di ku.

00:15:07.612 --> 00:15:09.061
kumt tsu geyn a shkheynete

00:15:09.061 --> 00:15:09.871
&lt;VOLODKA&gt;,

00:15:09.940 --> 00:15:11.760
zogt zi, "me hot derharget Simkhele."

00:15:11.760 --> 00:15:14.368
dos fun undz iz efsher kilometer, nit mer. bin ikh avek, gezen,

00:15:14.368 --> 00:15:16.196
iz er gelegn mit a tsehakte kop,

00:15:16.522 --> 00:15:17.428
a toyter.

00:15:17.940 --> 00:15:20.280
dos iz geven di ershte blut vos mir hobn derzen yidi-

00:15:20.235 --> 00:15:22.086
far vos er hot dos gemakht?

00:15:21.939 --> 00:15:25.443
far vos, er hot gevizn dem soldat di veg oyf, vi, vi iz, vu oyf Rige.

00:15:25.635 --> 00:15:27.573
vayl di gantse armey hot zikh getsoygn

00:15:27.609 --> 00:15:29.040
fun daytshishn grenets

00:15:29.040 --> 00:15:31.670
gegangen tsum letishn, tsum rusishn grenets.

00:15:31.878 --> 00:15:34.567
er gevart far daytshn, nit...

00:15:34.060 --> 00:15:34.650
&lt;KE?&gt;

00:15:34.567 --> 00:15:38.100
der, er iz shoyn gevart far daytshn, ikh farshtey azoy.

00:15:37.760 --> 00:15:38.560
ikh farshtey nit.

00:15:38.595 --> 00:15:42.471
der mentsh gevart far daytshn.

00:15:42.712 --> 00:15:44.731
ye, vayzt oys iz er, geveyntlekh, &lt;staytsh&gt;,

00:15:45.316 --> 00:15:46.405
dos iz geven zayn &lt;nor f-&gt;

00:15:46.405 --> 00:15:47.685
farbrekhn iz dos geven.

00:15:48.850 --> 00:15:50.047
montik,

00:15:51.858 --> 00:15:53.298
tsveytn halbn tog,

00:15:53.343 --> 00:15:54.977
zaynen mir shoyn aroys fun shtub,

00:15:54.977 --> 00:15:56.190
oder dinstik.

00:15:57.174 --> 00:15:58.411
zaynen mir aroys fun shtub

00:15:58.411 --> 00:15:59.205
vayle s'iz,

00:15:59.205 --> 00:16:01.390
ale hobn shoyn gevust &lt;UNK es&gt; kumt arayn der daytsh,

00:16:01.390 --> 00:16:04.492
veln mir vern farnikht. un andere shkheynim hobn gezogt "loyft!"

00:16:04.633 --> 00:16:05.963
vayl az s'kumt der daytsh vet aykh

00:16:05.963 --> 00:16:08.272
far aykh zayn de- nor an ort in vaser.

00:16:10.438 --> 00:16:12.305
zaynen mir aroysgegangen ale fun shtub.

00:16:13.526 --> 00:16:19.042
nor azoy vi bay undz iz geven a fir-vokhediker kind zaynen mir opgegangen nor in gantsn biz Meshkutsh, dos iz a kilometer akhtsn fun Shavl,

00:16:19.042 --> 00:16:21.131
un mer di shvegerin hot nit gekent geyn.

00:16:21.440 --> 00:16:23.235
zaynen zey geblibn in Meshkutsh,

00:16:23.235 --> 00:16:24.826
bay Yosl der Meshkutsher.

00:16:27.380 --> 00:16:28.944
dos iz geven shoyn dinstik

00:16:28.832 --> 00:16:31.898
ver gevezn der Yosl fu- ah MEŠKUIČIAI?

00:16:31.532 --> 00:16:33.280
a v-, a yid &lt;velkher hot&gt; gelebt in Meshkutsh.

00:16:33.280 --> 00:16:35.509
Yosl der Meshkutsher. azoy hot er zikh ongerufn.

00:16:34.097 --> 00:16:34.969
ir ge-

00:16:35.598 --> 00:16:37.854
ir geveyst im far di milkhome?

00:16:37.083 --> 00:16:39.990
mir hobn nit gevust, nor mir hobn gevust az es lebt dortn a Yosl Meshkutsher.

00:16:39.990 --> 00:16:41.291
nakher hot men im in Shavler turme

00:16:41.291 --> 00:16:42.565
derharget. dos shpeter

00:16:42.565 --> 00:16:43.389
vegn dem.

00:16:45.082 --> 00:16:46.674
dos iz geven, dinstik

00:16:46.674 --> 00:16:47.366
zaynen mir d-,

00:16:47.366 --> 00:16:49.307
mir zaynen gegangen montik dergangen biz im.

00:16:49.307 --> 00:16:50.927
dinstik iz ongeforn

00:16:50.938 --> 00:16:52.378
a laykhte mashin mit

00:16:52.378 --> 00:16:54.038
dray oder fir genereler

00:16:54.144 --> 00:16:55.415
fun der royter armey

00:16:55.443 --> 00:16:59.119
un &lt;nokh&gt; aroys&lt;geyn&gt; a general, hot zikh gebetn nokh vaser, zikh opgeshtelt lebn undz

00:16:59.139 --> 00:17:02.300
un geredt nor mit a gebrokhenem yidish, a rusishn gebrokhenem yidish.

00:17:02.300 --> 00:17:05.507
zogt er, "mayn mame," veynt, zogt er, "vos vet zayn mit undz, &lt;vos mit&gt; kleyne kinderlekh,

00:17:05.507 --> 00:17:06.430
&lt;zey&gt; veln derhargen."

00:17:06.430 --> 00:17:08.786
zogt er "veyn nit. mir'n zikh gikh kern tsurik."

00:17:09.180 --> 00:17:11.793
zaynen aropgeforn fun shtetl etlekhe hundert meter,

00:17:11.793 --> 00:17:13.123
hot men zey dershosn.

00:17:13.635 --> 00:17:15.367
fun a shtub hot men zey dershosn.

00:17:16.098 --> 00:17:18.103
UNK gekumen tsu loyfn mentshn; &lt;vi gezogt,&gt;

00:17:18.103 --> 00:17:20.176
m'hot dershosn di royte genereler.

00:17:21.549 --> 00:17:24.665
ver, ver dos dershosn, ver gekent d-

00:17:23.979 --> 00:17:25.149
fun a tsivile shtub.

00:17:25.149 --> 00:17:26.707
fun a litvishe tsivile shtub.

00:17:27.658 --> 00:17:29.256
ver hot geshosn hobn mir nit gezen.

00:17:30.240 --> 00:17:31.078
ikh hob...

00:17:31.337 --> 00:17:32.693
vi ikh hob dos derhert

00:17:32.693 --> 00:17:34.791
zog ikh tsu di mamen "ikh loyf.

00:17:36.095 --> 00:17:38.396
ikh loyf. ikh hob d- ikh loz dikh iber,

00:17:38.396 --> 00:17:39.431
un ikh loyf."

00:17:39.707 --> 00:17:41.169
di mame hot zikh tseveynt.

00:17:41.225 --> 00:17:44.291
ya gevelt lozn, nit gevelt lozn, der bruder zol, zol er loyfn.

00:17:44.668 --> 00:17:48.875
efsher vet er, er vet, efsher vet er zikh rateven. vayl mir hobn nit vu tsu loyfn, me ken di kinder nit varfn,

00:17:48.875 --> 00:17:52.031
hobn mir gekent geyn. un di mame k- &lt;ken nit&gt;, geven an eltere froy

00:17:52.076 --> 00:17:53.539
un nit keyn gezunte.

00:17:53.662 --> 00:17:56.712
un di shvester hot zi di mame nit gelozn geyn. di shvester iz in gantsn mayne geven

00:17:56.712 --> 00:18:00.072
tsvelf yor, draytsn yor iz zi geven. fun nayn un tsvantsikstn yor, iz zi geven tsvelf yor

00:18:00.072 --> 00:18:00.879
in gantsn.

00:18:01.560 --> 00:18:03.022
bin ikh aroys oyfn veg,

00:18:03.534 --> 00:18:04.788
oyfn shosey.

00:18:04.833 --> 00:18:06.239
Shavl, Yanishok,

00:18:06.239 --> 00:18:07.123
Rige.

00:18:08.141 --> 00:18:09.167
mentshn,

00:18:09.167 --> 00:18:10.636
di gantse veg iz geven f-

00:18:10.636 --> 00:18:12.894
ful mit mentshn. tsivile bafelkerung,

00:18:13.170 --> 00:18:14.745
un militer-layt.

00:18:14.756 --> 00:18:18.272
nu, di tsivile felker zaynen nor geven yidishe KONECHNO vayl di andere hobn nit gedarft loyfn.

00:18:18.272 --> 00:18:20.836
keyn andere relig- andere felker hobn nit ge-,

00:18:20.836 --> 00:18:24.200
hot &lt;dort dokh&gt; nit farnikht, gehat farnikhtik-, nit geven far neytik zey tsu loyfn.

00:18:24.442 --> 00:18:27.375
es flegn onflien daytshishe eroplanen iber di kep

00:18:27.378 --> 00:18:29.650
un varfn di kleyne SPLITTER-bombes

00:18:31.850 --> 00:18:33.737
un bashisn fun di koyln-varfer.

00:18:33.774 --> 00:18:38.370
un fun a beyde zayt az m'iz aroys oyfn veg, opgegangen a a tsvey kilometer, iz fun &lt;a beyde&gt; zaytn veg

00:18:38.370 --> 00:18:42.183
gelegn mentshn hot men geharget azoy vi, azoy vi beymer ongeshnitn in a vald.

00:18:42.183 --> 00:18:43.331
fun a beyde zaytn.

00:18:43.331 --> 00:18:47.187
un di veg iz gevorn a &lt;shmol&gt; UNK nor es hobn getsoygn zikh di soldatn hobn zikh getsoygn zikh,

00:18:47.187 --> 00:18:48.872
un di tsivile bafelkerung.

00:18:49.856 --> 00:18:51.364
mir zaynen opgegangen nit vayt,

00:18:51.364 --> 00:18:53.293
iz ongeforn tankistn.

00:18:54.277 --> 00:18:56.342
oyf di tankes iz geven nit-veynik mentshn,

00:18:56.342 --> 00:18:58.541
nor di kep hot zikh gezen fun di tankes.

00:18:59.829 --> 00:19:01.210
tsu m'hot im opgeshtelt dem

00:19:01.210 --> 00:19:03.215
k- &lt;ofitser&gt;, tsu s'hot zikh aleyn opgeshtelt,

00:19:03.457 --> 00:19:05.206
un hot undz zikh aroyfgenumen.

