nu, zey hobn, ver hot gekukt,

00:20:01.293 --> 00:20:03.057
ver hot gelakht, ver hot UNK

00:20:03.057 --> 00:20:04.809
ale far-, zey hobn mit undz nit avek.

00:20:05.203 --> 00:20:06.719
di velkhe zaynen mir gegangen

