a bisl gresere kinder, nor tsvey kinder geven &lt;kleyne&gt; mit vegelekh hobn gefirt, hobn mir zikh gebitn,

00:20:17.049 --> 00:20:19.085
geholfn di eltern firn di kinder

00:20:19.142 --> 00:20:20.301
mit vegelekh.

00:20:21.082 --> 00:20:24.148
mentshn umbakante; ikh ken nit zogn vayl es zaynen geven,

00:20:25.419 --> 00:20:26.797
un zaynen mir dergangen

00:20:27.090 --> 00:20:28.839
nit vayt fun JELGAVA.

00:20:29.115 --> 00:20:30.746
biz JELGAVA zaynen mir dergangen.

