gekert zikh tsurik, hobn mir hobn zikh ge- gegebn a drey

00:21:51.276 --> 00:21:56.761
links, iz gelozn JELGAVA rekhts, un mir UNK mit a mol dortn UNK me zogt dortn iz do a brikl UNK,

00:21:56.761 --> 00:21:59.239
m'iz gekumen dortn, dortn oykh di zelbike.

00:21:59.312 --> 00:22:00.549
nit aribertsugeyn.

00:22:00.560 --> 00:22:02.731
mentshn hobn gebetn lotkes fardingen.

00:22:03.007 --> 00:22:04.616
m'hot gevelt avekgebn ringen.

00:22:04.616 --> 00:22:06.363
zog dortn di balebatim, di letn,

00:22:06.363 --> 00:22:10.275
lotkes veln mir gebn nor me vet nit ariber, dort fun yene zayt shteyen oykhet koyln-varfer tsugegreyte.

00:22:10.415 --> 00:22:12.615
der gantser vaser iz geven fun yene, hot farnumen

00:22:12.626 --> 00:22:14.893
der, der, der brik fun vaser,

00:22:14.893 --> 00:22:16.907
iz geven farnumen di letishe partizaner.

00:22:24.607 --> 00:22:28.449
nor azoy, az s'iz keyn ander veg nit geblibn, zikh kern tsurik in Shavl.

00:22:29.822 --> 00:22:31.909
hob ikh zikh gekert tsurik in Shavl.

00:22:32.673 --> 00:22:37.935
vifl di veg hot mir gedoyert ken ikh aykh nit zogn; ikh bin durkh Yanishok tsurik un durkh di zelbe veg &lt;oyf vanet&gt; ikh bin gegangen.

00:22:37.938 --> 00:22:39.603
ikh bin ongegangen in Meshkutsh

00:22:39.761 --> 00:22:41.462
vu &lt;iz&gt; gehat gelozn di mamen,

00:22:41.465 --> 00:22:42.641
dem bruder

00:22:42.798 --> 00:22:43.884
un zayn familye.

00:22:43.884 --> 00:22:45.049
hot men undz geentfert

00:22:45.077 --> 00:22:47.116
az zey zaynen avek karik oyf Shavl

00:22:47.118 --> 00:22:48.783
un Yosl iz shoyn arestirt.

00:22:48.958 --> 00:22:51.315
der balebos, f-, fun Meshkutsher yid.

00:22:52.620 --> 00:22:57.019
bin ikh gekumen biz Shavl, iz di ershte vos mit mir glaykh UNK kumen arayn in Shavl,

00:22:57.227 --> 00:22:58.852
hob ikh getrofn &lt;UNK&gt;n

00:22:58.852 --> 00:23:00.073
un ŠNARISn.

00:23:00.230 --> 00:23:04.156
az zey hobn dershosn Mazovetskin. dos iz di greste, di greste nayes hot mir ibergegebn.

00:23:04.753 --> 00:23:06.486
ver gevezn der...

00:23:05.681 --> 00:23:08.159
Mazovetski iz geven dokh undzer a shokhn, a beker.

00:23:08.178 --> 00:23:09.776
er hot nit vayt fun undz gelebt.

00:23:10.254 --> 00:23:11.846
der farbrekhn zayner iz geven dos

00:23:11.846 --> 00:23:12.867
az er fleg bakn

00:23:12.867 --> 00:23:15.651
besere broyt vi ŠNARIS. ŠNARIS iz a litvishe familye.

00:23:15.651 --> 00:23:18.647
zi hot UNK gehat di bekeray. flegt bay zey veynik ver koyfn, der flegt merer koyfn.

00:23:18.647 --> 00:23:21.504
dos iz &lt;geven&gt; di ershte nayes &lt;vi der Simkhe&gt; hot mir dertseylt.

00:23:22.725 --> 00:23:24.426
nu, ikh bin gekumen in shtub.

00:23:24.426 --> 00:23:25.419
di mame hot zikh

00:23:25.475 --> 00:23:27.343
i derfreyt, i tseveynt.

00:23:27.635 --> 00:23:31.544
derfreyt az ikh bin geblibn, az zi hot tseveynt far vos mir hobn gekert, nit gekent avekgeyn vayter.

00:23:32.310 --> 00:23:33.311
in der tsayt

00:23:33.311 --> 00:23:35.713
hot zikh shoyn in Shavl gegosn blut vi vaser.

00:23:36.663 --> 00:23:38.677
Vilner gas iz geven mer a yidishe gas.

00:23:38.677 --> 00:23:41.585
iz shoyn aroysgegangen UNK a sakh mentshn, nokh Vilner gas iz geven.

00:23:42.300 --> 00:23:43.723
nokh Vilner. az ikh bin gekumen in Shavl

00:23:43.723 --> 00:23:47.458
hot zikh gemuzt zayn arum zuntik oder efsher montik, shoyn a vokh tsayt vi &lt;s'iz shoyn&gt; avek,

00:23:47.531 --> 00:23:49.905
fun der tsayt heyst dos vi ikh bin aroys fun shtub.

00:23:50.973 --> 00:23:54.573
un dos vos &lt;m'hot aroys glaykh&gt; di tragedye. in Shavl iz geven, gelebt a yunge f-

00:23:54.573 --> 00:23:56.807
familye, &lt;zi hot&gt; zeyer a sheyne meydele

00:23:57.150 --> 00:23:58.514
nit ke- nit keyn

00:23:58.514 --> 00:23:59.687
tsutsu&lt;UNK&gt; tsu keynem.

00:23:59.687 --> 00:24:02.038
zaynen gegangen shabes in shul mit di kind.

00:24:02.111 --> 00:24:03.543
hot men ir azoy farhaltn

00:24:03.543 --> 00:24:07.373
oyfn gas un m'hot di meydl ibergerisn in tsvey teyln un avekgelofn di mame unter di fis

00:24:07.373 --> 00:24:08.597
tsvey shtiker

00:24:08.642 --> 00:24:09.970
az UNK &lt;kind&gt;.

00:24:10.515 --> 00:24:12.079
dos iz geven in Shavl,

00:24:12.185 --> 00:24:14.528
un ot aza min tragedye iz geven in Kovne, Aleksot.

00:24:14.528 --> 00:24:17.951
dos hobn mentshn lebedikerheyt UNK dos gezen, vos m'hot mir dertseylt.

00:24:19.391 --> 00:24:20.375
un Shavl UNK

00:24:20.375 --> 00:24:21.354
vos tut men?

00:24:21.365 --> 00:24:23.632
blut gist zikh. keyn farteydikung iz nito.

00:24:23.677 --> 00:24:25.477
nor azoy vi mir hobn gelebt oyfn dorf,

00:24:25.550 --> 00:24:28.261
un undzere shkheynim zaynen geven ruiker, neytrale mentshn.

00:24:28.368 --> 00:24:30.062
perzenlekh undz hot men nit fartshepet.

00:24:30.062 --> 00:24:31.789
undz hot men afile keyn gloz nit oysgehakt

00:24:32.098 --> 00:24:33.341
fun undzere shkheynim.

00:24:33.431 --> 00:24:35.940
nor in shtot, iz fun shtot iz &lt;di geslekh&gt; shoyn gegosn in blut.

00:24:36.215 --> 00:24:37.874
nit kukndik &lt;oyf&gt; dos vos Shavl

00:24:37.874 --> 00:24:41.933
tsutsuglaykhn kegn andere shtet fun Lite, tsum bayshpil, Kovne,

00:24:41.936 --> 00:24:43.483
Maryampole, Lite,

00:24:43.725 --> 00:24:47.586
Maryampole, MARIJAMPOLĖ, Lite s- iz geven eyne fun di ruikste kegn yidn.

00:24:47.586 --> 00:24:49.659
dos blut hot zikh gegosn vi vaser.

00:24:51.487 --> 00:24:52.610
eyn- antshuldikung. UNK

00:24:59.047 --> 00:25:00.729
dertseylt nokh dem.

00:25:01.157 --> 00:25:03.480
dos vos s'hot zikh shoyn blut gegosn vi vaser.

00:25:03.806 --> 00:25:07.040
azoy bin ikh opgeven a kurtse tsayt in, in

00:25:07.468 --> 00:25:08.593
in Shavl

