undz flegt men araynshtupn

00:25:57.333 --> 00:25:59.606
tsvey fir familyes in eyn tsimer.

00:26:00.573 --> 00:26:04.249
tsv- tsvey fir fa-. ot aza tsimer umgefer bay undz iz a zibetsn kvadrat

